description:
This ti was requested by @dav231 and @lwdm22

Alia Bhatt is an Indian actress and singer who primarily works in Hindi films. She made her acting debut in 2012 with the film "Student of the Year," directed by Karan Johar. Alia has since appeared in a variety of successful films across different genres and has garnered critical acclaim for her performances. Some of her notable movies include "Highway" (2014), "Udta Punjab" (2016), "Dear Zindagi" (2016), "Raazi" (2018), and "Gully Boy" (2019). Apart from acting, Alia Bhatt has also showcased her singing skills in several films. She has sung songs for movies like "Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania" (2014), "Badrinath Ki Dulhania" (2017), and "Dear Zindagi" (2016).
